name metago
category Package
revision 78101
shortdesc MetaPost output of Go positions
longdesc The package allows you to draw Go game positions with MetaPost.
longdesc Two methods of usage are provided, either using the package
longdesc programmatically, or using the package via a script (which may
longdesc produce several images).
